EU Plans to Involve Investors in Bank Rescues, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-09-27T07:03:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/eu-plans-to-involve-investors-in-bank-rescues-handelsblatt-says.html
European Financial Services
Commissioner  Michel Barnier  plans to involve shareholders and
creditors in future bank rescues,  Germany ’s  Handelsblatt 
newspaper reported, citing a draft law.  Investors have to shoulder an “appropriate” part of the
losses, according to the draft. National banking supervisors
should be given the right to write down or delete shares, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  